     7→ * - Frustum culling: Only renders tasks visible in the viewport
     8→ * - InstancedMesh for grid lines: Single draw call instead of ~251 meshes
     9→ * - Lazy label rendering: Only labels for visible tasks
    10→ * - InstancedMesh for row backgrounds: Single draw call instead of 50 meshes
    11→ */
