   625→        transparent
   626→        opacity={0.4 * opacity}
   627→      />
   628→    </instancedMesh>
   629→  );
   630→}
   631→
   632→/**
   633→ * MicroLayer Component
   634→ *
   635→ * Optimized for performance with:
   636→ * - Frustum culling for tasks
   637→ * - InstancedMesh for grid lines and row backgrounds
   638→ * - Limited HTML labels (max 50)
   639→ * - Dependency lines between tasks (F023)
