    11→ *
    12→ * Usage:
    13→ * ```tsx
    14→ * const { store, isLoaded, getTask, taskCount } = useEntityStore(tasks);
    15→ * ```
    16→ *
    17→ * Architecture notes:
    18→ * - EntityStore is Simulation State (60fps, direct access)
    19→ * - @zazcart/tools is UI State (event-driven, reactive)
    20→ * - This hook bridges the two: EntityStore data → React components
